title: Indumathi
subTitle: A group of friends rent out a place for spending some fun time together. However, they are unaware that there is a psychopathic killer on the loose.

title: Mawali: Ek Play Boy
subTitle: After a wealthy businessman meets with an accident, his daughter takes over his company. However, her skills are tested when she has to spot the imposter who is out to destroy her father's company.

title: Arjun Gowda
subTitle: Arjun is a hot-headed young man who will do anything for the people he loves. When a figure from the underworld threatens his loved ones, he springs into action.

title: Jeene Do - Let Us Live
subTitle: An up-and-coming cyclist arrives in Mumbai for the final round of a championship. But his life takes a 180 degree turn when he discovers his family's painful past and sets out to avenge them.

title: Nagashaurya's Aswathama
subTitle: A man returns to India for his sister's engagement ceremony but discovers that something terrible has happened to her. On his quest for the truth, he uncovers a series of crimes against women.

title: Main Hi Raja Main Hi Mantri
subTitle: A moneylender is living a happily married life. However, when his wife is insulted by the village sarpanch's wife, he focuses all of his energy on becoming a powerful politician.

title: Garam
subTitle: Varala, a jobless young man, leaves his home to prove himself to his father. However, before achieving his goal, he falls in love with Sameera and tries to woo and save her from gangster Biju.

title: Captain
subTitle: A captain leads his team of soldiers inside a forest to investigate mysterious disappearances. However, they soon realise that the danger is more than they bargain for.

title: Rudhran
subTitle: A man's life takes an unexpected turn when he stumbles upon a criminal network. Determined to bring the truth to light, he sets out to expose the nefarious organisation and protect his loved ones.

title: God Father
subTitle: An unforeseen event forces a single father and former gangster striving for a peaceful life back into the world of crime.

title: Gabbar Is Back
subTitle: The city's administration wrongs Aditya, a commoner. To avenge his tragedy, he disguises himself as a vigilante, Gabbar, and teams up with honest government officers to expose the corrupt.

title: Dum Man Of Power
subTitle: Tarak comes to India after his parents die in an accident and falls in love with Meera, who seeks others' happiness before hers. Soon, Tarak and Meera's relationship goes through a rough patch.

title: Dum Man Of Power

title: Friday The 13th
subTitle: The 13th page of a mysterious book harbours evil. It gives rise to a series of devastating events as people who read it, get possessed by demonic spirits.

title: Khakee
subTitle: A deputy commissioner and his crew attempt to transport a terrorist to Mumbai, but their mission is thwarted by an ex-policeman with an agenda of his own.

title: Sivudu
subTitle: A carefree young man's life is disrupted by rising crime in his locality and when his family faces danger, he decides to fight back.

title: Bal Ganesh
subTitle: Bal Ganesh, the mischievous son of Lord Shiva, embarks on several adventures with Mooshak the mouse, his friend and vehicle. Despite being young, he battles evil forces and protects the world.

title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Veera Simha Reddy
subTitle: Jai Simha Reddy, the son of the esteemed Veera Simha Reddy, returns home to avenge his father's death as a result of village politics.

title: Inspector Vijay
subTitle: Vijay, an honest police officer, meets Samyukta at a cafe and falls in love with her. However, his life changes when he witnesses a kidnapping and ends up helping a lonely woman, Lavanya.

title: Zombie Reddy
subTitle: Chaos ensue as Mario, a game developer, and his gang of friends get entangled in a family feud and an enigmatic zombie attack in Rayalaseema, while attending a friend's wedding.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: Sangharsh Aur Vijay
subTitle: Badri is the protector of Badrinath temple. However, when a woman falls in love with him, his guru decides against making Badri his successor.

title: Don
subTitle: Chakaravarthi, a wayward college student searching for purpose, navigates campus life while grappling with a controlling father and a strict professor.

title: Don

title: Surya Ka Yaarana
subTitle: A soldier going on a rescue mission, hears about his father's death by lung cancer and mournfully looks back on his memories of how he helped him in matters of love and life.

title: Jigar Kaleja
subTitle: A short tempered cab driver, Raju, unwillingly becomes the saviour of a village. When an industrialist tries to drive away the villagers by polluting their water and air, Raju steps up to help them.

title: Inttelligent
subTitle: A successful software engineer becomes a vigilante following the demise of his mentor in a bid to seek revenge against those responsible for the latter's death.

title: Main Hoon Dandadhikari
subTitle: Following his father's death, a man gives up on his dream to become a film-maker and joins the police force. He then attempts to track down a psychopathic killer who targets schoolgirls.

title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Guardian
subTitle: An unavenged woman returns from the dead to terrify and terrorise those who tormented her when she was alive.

title: Gally Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Ek Aur Vinashak
subTitle: An honest man is forced to turn into a gangster as he strives to make enough money for the treatment of a girl who is comatose.
